{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"3668","text":"The existence of the evil cannot be explained with the human freedom","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3669","text":"There are evils whose occurrence has no discernible connection with freedom.  Theologians call them natural evils meaning such things as earthquakes floods tornadoes diseases and so on.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3670","text":"We weren't around then","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3671","text":"If a deer dies in a forest fire suffering horribly as it does so that is an evil.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3672","text":"If evil is in the world only for the human freedom all the evil is connected to the human freedom","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3673","text":"none of it seems beyond the power of omnipotence to prevent without the loss of that good.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3674","text":"if you accept anything like the theory of evolution you will believe there were other animals on this planet long before humans appeared on the scene","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3675","text":"Many of them must have suffered horribly as their species became extinct.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:55"},{"nodeID":"3676","text":"None of that suffering can be justified as a necessary consequence of permitting humans freedom.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:56"},{"nodeID":"3677","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:56","scheme":"Example","schemeID":"14"},{"nodeID":"3678","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:56","scheme":"CauseToEffect","schemeID":"4"},{"nodeID":"3679","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:56","scheme":"FalsificationOfHypothesis","schemeID":"16"},{"nodeID":"3680","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:57","scheme":"FalsificationOfHypothesis","schemeID":"16"},{"nodeID":"3681","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:29:57","scheme":"CauseToEffect","schemeID":"4"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"3472","fromID":"3669","toID":"3677","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3473","fromID":"3677","toID":"3671","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3474","fromID":"3670","toID":"3678","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3475","fromID":"3678","toID":"3676","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3476","fromID":"3671","toID":"3679","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3477","fromID":"3672","toID":"3679","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3478","fromID":"3679","toID":"3668","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3479","fromID":"3673","toID":"3680","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3480","fromID":"3672","toID":"3680","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3481","fromID":"3680","toID":"3668","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3482","fromID":"3674","toID":"3681","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3483","fromID":"3675","toID":"3681","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3484","fromID":"3676","toID":"3681","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"3485","fromID":"3681","toID":"3673","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[]}